# File Structure Guide

## Key Directories

### Content Directories
- **[docs/](mdc:docs)** - Main documentation with tutorials and guides
  - **[docs/tutorial-basics/](mdc:docs/tutorial-basics)** - Core LoRaWAN tutorials (numbered 001-009)
  - **[docs/tutorial-extras/](mdc:docs/tutorial-extras)** - Advanced topics and integrations
  - **[docs/codecs/](mdc:docs/codecs)** - Device codec documentation
- **[blog/](mdc:blog)** - Industry articles and technical blog posts
- **[static/](mdc:static)** - Static assets (images, files, scripts)

### Source Code
- **[src/components/](mdc:src/components)** - Reusable React components
  - **[src/components/HomepageFeatures/](mdc:src/components/HomepageFeatures)** - Homepage feature cards
  - **[src/components/InfoPanes/](mdc:src/components/InfoPanes)** - Information display components
- **[src/pages/](mdc:src/pages)** - Custom pages (about, contact, etc.)
- **[src/css/](mdc:src/css)** - Custom styling and CSS variables

### Configuration
- **[docusaurus.config.js](mdc:docusaurus.config.js)** - Main Docusaurus configuration
- **[sidebars.js](mdc:sidebars.js)** - Documentation sidebar structure
- **[package.json](mdc:package.json)** - Dependencies and npm scripts
- **[vercel.json](mdc:vercel.json)** - Vercel deployment configuration

### Assets Organization
- **[static/images/](mdc:static/images)** - Tutorial and documentation images
- **[static/img/](mdc:static/img)** - Branding, icons, and media assets
- **[static/flows/](mdc:static/flows)** - Node-RED flow JSON files
- **[static/scripts/](mdc:static/scripts)** - Installation and utility scripts

### Utility Scripts
- **[scripts/](mdc:scripts)** - Build and optimization scripts
- **[extra_admin/](mdc:extra_admin)** - Administrative files and backups
